{
  "stem": "323.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then when we-- all of a sudden, we heard this announcement that the Allied forces have entered the concentration camp, and the-- we should hold, and food will be coming, we should hold on.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that point, I was so sick I didn't care anymore.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Food came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that make me sicker, because I ate the food that I wasn't used to.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then the medic people came in to take-- to treat all the sick.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they decided-- since I was a German Jew, they wouldn't take care of me because I was German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm hm.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All I remember is this announcement.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I-- I understand that most of the soldiers got sick just looking at us, and looking to see what was there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they set up these soup kitchens, and bread, and then-- I-- I was too sick.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I just-- I couldn't do anything else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't move anymore.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh huh.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably the end of April, early May.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I decided, well, you see, I still had this with me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, they don't want to treat me as a German?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I'll become a Czech.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went back, and I said, I'm Czech, and they treated me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So because I was with all these Czech people anyhow.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said, well, I'll be Czech.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then I remember that I had to leave all my clothes behind.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They put me on a stretcher.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They carried me, and they had doctors examining me, and they put me into an infirmary, and I was taken care of by French nuns.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was completely out of it for about a week.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
